      "name": "Mesh convergence study — FDA centrifugal pump",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse 1.2M, medium 3.8M, fine 9.1M elements) performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at 2500 RPM, 5 L/min. GCI-based discretization error estimated at 2.3% for wall shear stress and 1.8% for velocity magnitude at the impeller outlet. Fine mesh adopted for production runs.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
