    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate mean absolute relative error of 8.4% against FDA benchmark data, with RH < 1 confirmed for the worst-case operating condition. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the defined COU.",
